				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Mass Kiting - Feedback Requested!!<a name="19885"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 9 04 5:56 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>AE kiting will serve you well, its a great way to get fast xp.
<br />

<br />
However, one word of warning - do remember to try other things out too - group with others around your level, use your melee skills, get hit sometimes and so forth. Otherwise, you will find that your character's skills lag severely behind your level. This can be particularly true for defense, which directly affects (quite severely) your AC rating, and your weapon skills which equates to your melee dps.
<br />

<br />
Like all good things, use only in moderation ;)</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
